WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: Reh7Q-loWtQ

NOTE Language: en

00:00:01.160 --> 00:00:14.000
With today’s vibrations, you can see, when
you are prepared for a puja, how much you get.

00:00:14.090 --> 00:00:20.890
Today you can feel it.

00:00:20.890 --> 00:00:28.869
So the Divine is very anxious to act, only
thing you have to prepare yourself.

00:00:28.869 --> 00:00:34.880
And all these preparations are going to help
you tremendously.

00:00:34.880 --> 00:00:45.170
As we are now Sahaja Yogis we have to know
that we have become something different from

00:00:45.170 --> 00:00:46.910
what we were.

00:00:46.910 --> 00:00:53.070
We are Yogis, we are higher people than others.

00:00:53.070 --> 00:01:03.150
And as such we have to understand one thing
that we are not like other human beings who

00:01:03.150 --> 00:01:07.450
say something and do something, who can live
with hypocrisy.

00:01:07.450 --> 00:01:16.710
That’s why all the problems have arisen
out of all the religions.

00:01:16.710 --> 00:01:22.789
A person who says he’s a Christian he’s
absolutely anti-Christ; who says who is Islamic,

00:01:22.789 --> 00:01:34.329
he’s absolutely anti-Mohammed; who says
who is a Hindu is absolutely anti Shri Krishna.

00:01:34.329 --> 00:01:43.130
This is the main reason why all the religions
have failed so far because human beings talk

00:01:43.130 --> 00:01:48.270
big of ideals.

00:01:48.270 --> 00:01:53.749
They all say that we have this ideal, that
ideal, but they are not those ideals, they

00:01:53.749 --> 00:01:54.749
cannot live with those ideals.

00:01:54.749 --> 00:02:01.420
The ideals are not in their lives, they’re
outside.

00:02:01.420 --> 00:02:09.270
But they go about saying that these are our
ideals, they become fanatics but they are

00:02:09.270 --> 00:02:12.830
not the ideals.

00:02:12.830 --> 00:02:20.920
By Sahaja Yoga now you have the method, you
have the possibility, that you can become

00:02:20.920 --> 00:02:21.980
the ideals.

00:02:21.980 --> 00:02:30.840
The ideal has to first to be understood through
your brains, in the West specially.

00:02:30.840 --> 00:02:37.910
What are the ideals we have become or we have
to become, what we can achieve, this idea

00:02:37.910 --> 00:02:39.540
you must have.

00:02:39.540 --> 00:02:54.320
And secondly you must have a capacity to deepen
your

00:02:54.320 --> 00:03:00.450
meditative power so that these ideals go and
settle in your heart as a part and parcel

00:03:00.450 --> 00:03:06.030
of your being, that you can’t live without
these ideals.

00:03:06.030 --> 00:03:10.111
We can take an example say of Christ.

00:03:10.111 --> 00:03:17.700
For Christ He and His ideals were the same,
there’s no difference between them.

00:03:17.700 --> 00:03:22.450
He did not talk of one thing, did another
thing and executed the third.

00:03:22.450 --> 00:03:29.790
This will be the difference between the Sahaja
Yogis and non Sahaja Yogis, that whatever

00:03:29.790 --> 00:03:36.960
are your ideals have to be expressed in your
life every moment because you are that.

00:03:36.960 --> 00:03:43.000
If you are gold, then gold is gold all the
time.

00:03:43.000 --> 00:03:50.760
It is not gold sometimes, then sometimes iron
and sometimes mud, it is gold all the time.

00:03:50.760 --> 00:03:59.760
Only human beings are like that, that sometimes
they can be snakes, lions and could be foxes

00:03:59.760 --> 00:04:02.010
also.

00:04:02.010 --> 00:04:11.870
But as Sahaja Yogis you become pure human
beings and this is what we have to know.

00:04:11.870 --> 00:04:17.810
It is not difficult to strive for it, it’s
not difficult, because now you have the power

00:04:17.810 --> 00:04:23.510
to deepen your roots to your heart.

00:04:23.510 --> 00:04:32.260
So the brain must be used to understand clearly
what are the ideals of a Sahaja Yogi.

00:04:32.260 --> 00:04:40.510
What are the things that a Sahaja Yogi should
do, how he should behave in life, what methods

00:04:40.510 --> 00:04:46.750
he should follow.

00:04:46.750 --> 00:04:57.699
And then he has to bring it to his heart through
meditative processes, through surrendering.

00:04:57.699 --> 00:05:01.070
How I give you second birth you know very
well.

00:05:01.070 --> 00:05:05.910
I conceive you in My heart, otherwise I cannot
do it.

00:05:05.910 --> 00:05:13.460
Because My heart is so pure, it cleanses you;
by compassion My love cleanses you and then

00:05:13.460 --> 00:05:25.180
I can take you out of My Sahastrara, otherwise
how will I do that?

00:05:25.180 --> 00:05:33.600
And when that is happened you have become
a new personality.

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:41.400
So you are very different from all others
because a Spirit has given birth to your Spirit.

00:05:41.400 --> 00:05:48.730
You have been cleansed by the Spirit.

00:05:48.730 --> 00:05:56.160
So you cannot live like that, like all other
human beings are living.

00:05:56.160 --> 00:06:04.730
All the clashes, all the problems of human
beings are because they are not what they

00:06:04.730 --> 00:06:16.110
talk, ideals are out, out of their life.

00:06:16.110 --> 00:06:22.230
That is how a Sahaja Yogi will show himself
off compared to anybody else.

00:06:22.230 --> 00:06:27.370
Take an example say of Abraham Lincoln, all
right?

00:06:27.370 --> 00:06:33.300
Abraham Lincoln believed that everybody must
have freedom and the government should be

00:06:33.300 --> 00:06:36.380
for the public, for the people.

00:06:36.380 --> 00:06:41.910
Whatever He talked He practised it.

00:06:41.910 --> 00:06:50.300
Whatever He believed in He worked it out and
gave His life for it, that’s why He’s

00:06:50.300 --> 00:06:51.740
a great man.

00:06:51.740 --> 00:06:56.520
Think of Mahatma Gandhi, they were not like
Christ – incarnations.

00:06:56.520 --> 00:07:04.860
Think of any great man, think of Shivaji Maharaj,
any one of the saints – they were human

00:07:04.860 --> 00:07:05.860
beings.

00:07:05.860 --> 00:07:12.570
But once they knew this is the principle on
which we have to live, they become one with

00:07:12.570 --> 00:07:15.020
the principles, they do not compromise.

00:07:15.020 --> 00:07:27.150
So what Sahaja Yogi has to be that we should
understand.

00:07:27.150 --> 00:07:35.350
A Sahaja Yogi is a person who has got Realization
through the Kundalini, and Kundalini is the

00:07:35.350 --> 00:07:43.470
motherhood in you, is the caring, nourishing
power within you.

00:07:43.470 --> 00:07:48.160
But mother will never compromise with the
son; if he wants to kill somebody she’ll

00:07:48.160 --> 00:07:49.160
say: “No.

00:07:49.160 --> 00:07:50.560
” I mean a real mother.

00:07:50.560 --> 00:07:54.970
She will even shoot that son who tries to
do wrong things.

00:07:54.970 --> 00:08:06.689
In the same way if you become the mother of
yourself, then you have to look after yourself,

00:08:06.689 --> 00:08:13.910
in the same manner that you nourish yourself
and all others also, you have to nourish them,

00:08:13.910 --> 00:08:21.120
care for them, and do not compromise with
wrong doings, unrighteousness things, absurd

00:08:21.120 --> 00:08:22.120
things.

00:08:22.120 --> 00:08:31.580
Now when I tell you this it is not necessary
for you to feel guilty.

00:08:31.580 --> 00:08:37.099
We have to look upward.

00:08:37.099 --> 00:08:48.200
Those who are standing even on a lower staircase,
if they are looking upward they are all right,

00:08:48.200 --> 00:08:58.890
but those who are standing at a higher steps,
and looking downward, will go down.

00:08:58.890 --> 00:09:01.399
So look forward.

00:09:01.399 --> 00:09:09.470
What we have to do in our day-to-day life
in simple relationships even husband, wife,

00:09:09.470 --> 00:09:13.890
children, parents – are you becoming silent
within yourself?

00:09:13.890 --> 00:09:22.580
Are you nourishing it, with your silence,
with your compassion, or you are supporting

00:09:22.580 --> 00:09:28.620
something that is absolutely anti-God?

00:09:28.620 --> 00:09:35.700
If you become the ideals, the power of ideals
itself, will make you so dynamic that you

00:09:35.700 --> 00:09:42.420
don’t need to consult anybody, you become
the ideal.

00:09:42.420 --> 00:09:47.350
They are like torches.

00:09:47.350 --> 00:09:52.920
Your ideals itself will be enlightened.

00:09:52.920 --> 00:09:57.190
So the first attitude should be: “How do
we deepen ourselves?”

00:09:57.190 --> 00:09:59.170
That should be first attitude.

00:09:59.170 --> 00:10:06.580
Now say a husband, wife are quarrelling morning
till evening they cannot be Sahaja Yogis.

00:10:06.580 --> 00:10:08.150
Absurdities.

00:10:08.150 --> 00:10:14.270
If they are quarrelling they are not Sahaja
Yogis, take it for granted.

00:10:14.270 --> 00:10:18.990
Now what you have to do if two persons are
quarrelling, the one who is a Sahaja Yogi

00:10:18.990 --> 00:10:23.180
will leave that wife: “I have nothing to
do with wife, I have no wife nothing.

00:10:23.180 --> 00:10:25.730
” Keep out, detach completely from within.

00:10:25.730 --> 00:10:27.550
Just don’t talk to that wife.

00:10:27.550 --> 00:10:32.490
Don’t discuss, don’t bother about it,
just detach.

00:10:32.490 --> 00:10:47.589
If the son is like that just detach, up to
a point but no quarrelling, no argument nothing.

00:10:47.589 --> 00:10:55.850
Complete silence, a silent protest, must be
developed.

00:10:55.850 --> 00:10:58.730
But in that silence you should not be a cowardly
person.

00:10:58.730 --> 00:11:06.810
So many people are cowards, and that cowardliness,
they think is their silent process.

00:11:06.810 --> 00:11:21.970
A person who is really powerful will not deter,
will not be aggressive but will not also take

00:11:21.970 --> 00:11:24.560
aggression.

00:11:24.560 --> 00:11:30.680
So in your meditations you have to sit down.

00:11:30.680 --> 00:11:34.589
Now what do you say in meditation?

00:11:34.589 --> 00:11:37.280
Try to see all the chakras.

00:11:37.280 --> 00:11:41.890
What chakras are catching, face it yourself.

00:11:41.890 --> 00:11:45.580
These might be from your past life.

00:11:45.580 --> 00:11:49.470
Some chakras are weak.

00:11:49.470 --> 00:11:55.320
Try to make them all right, try to strengthen
them.

00:11:55.320 --> 00:12:01.200
Because ideals have to be worked out the instrument
has to be all right.

00:12:01.200 --> 00:12:11.310
If the instrument is a crazy one how will
you do?

00:12:11.310 --> 00:12:17.060
So first of all you must develop your instrument
properly, it should be balanced, powerful,

00:12:17.060 --> 00:12:19.450
not cowardly.

00:12:19.450 --> 00:12:24.190
People should feel your power.

00:12:24.190 --> 00:12:31.720
Of course the power is of love, but love doesn’t
mean that you compromise with all the nonsensical

00:12:31.720 --> 00:12:32.720
things.

00:12:32.720 --> 00:12:38.029
There should be no compromise at all.

00:12:38.029 --> 00:12:47.130
It’s a very self-certifying state.

00:12:47.130 --> 00:12:53.470
We cannot say when it is so, we just cannot
say.

00:12:53.470 --> 00:12:59.480
Itself the state will certify that I’m all
right now, I have reached that state.

00:12:59.480 --> 00:13:08.680
We cannot say after five hours, three minutes,
two seconds you’ll become that.

00:13:08.680 --> 00:13:17.930
You just mature and you see that maturity
within you.

00:13:17.930 --> 00:13:24.100
Once you understand that unless and until
you become your ideals you are not a Sahaja

00:13:24.100 --> 00:13:25.300
Yogi.

00:13:25.300 --> 00:13:28.899
Everybody can call themselves Sahaja Yogis,
there’s not inauguration, we don’t have

00:13:28.899 --> 00:13:42.050
any sort of a – inauguration of a university
where people can come and get their degrees

00:13:42.050 --> 00:13:45.960
and diplomas: “All right you are certified
twice born.

00:13:45.960 --> 00:13:52.800
” There are some who are several times twice
born.

00:13:52.800 --> 00:13:57.120
They are twice born today, tomorrow they are
not, then again they come twice born and again

00:13:57.120 --> 00:13:58.120
twice born.

00:13:58.120 --> 00:14:05.220
Some of them can be one hundred and eight
times twice born in Sahaja Yoga.

00:14:05.220 --> 00:14:08.250
And even then they are not certified.

00:14:08.250 --> 00:14:11.130
So you have to give yourself a certificate.

00:14:11.130 --> 00:14:17.350
There’s no university to do that.

00:14:17.350 --> 00:14:22.019
You have to understand yourself, what are
your problems, why you are behaving like this?

00:14:22.019 --> 00:14:24.470
You treat yourself as a child.

00:14:24.470 --> 00:14:28.709
When it is needed you have to rebuke yourself.

00:14:28.709 --> 00:14:32.050
When you have to glorify, you should glorify
yourself.

00:14:32.050 --> 00:14:34.970
So now you separate.

00:14:34.970 --> 00:14:40.390
You become the mother, the Spirit is the mother,
and you, whatever you are which has to grow,

00:14:40.390 --> 00:14:42.760
is the child.

00:14:42.760 --> 00:14:54.190
Mother is the ideal, she is the inspiration,
she is the power, and the child is the recipient.

00:14:54.190 --> 00:14:59.440
If the child is an obstinate fellow then you
can’t do anything about it.

00:14:59.440 --> 00:15:01.980
Also find out – you might be one of them.

00:15:01.980 --> 00:15:03.310
I know who are they like that.

00:15:03.310 --> 00:15:09.390
There are many and you can find them out in
no time.

00:15:09.390 --> 00:15:19.100
Obstinate fellows, if they live with ten people
suddenly we hear reports of their existence.

00:15:19.100 --> 00:15:26.100
They are quite eloquent even if they are not
talking a word people can tell you: “I had

00:15:26.100 --> 00:15:30.450
a fight with such and such.

00:15:30.450 --> 00:15:36.150
That person said such and such a thing to
me, that person was so cruel to me, that person

00:15:36.150 --> 00:15:37.880
demanded this.

00:15:37.880 --> 00:15:40.470
” You know which person it is, where.

00:15:40.470 --> 00:15:44.880
You see as a diamond can be made out thorns
can be made out, also anytime you go near

00:15:44.880 --> 00:15:50.310
the thorn, anyone without exception, it will
bite everyone.

00:15:50.310 --> 00:15:53.300
It is not going to spare, it’s a thorn.

00:15:53.300 --> 00:15:56.720
So a thorn has to be a thorn.

00:15:56.720 --> 00:16:06.360
But if you are a Sahaja Yogi you have to be
a flower and a strong flower and an eternal

00:16:06.360 --> 00:16:10.870
flower, that always grows, does not fade out.

00:16:10.870 --> 00:16:19.300
Always growing, never fades, such a flower
you have to be, then you will be surprised

00:16:19.300 --> 00:16:38.100
that you do not get into a trip of ego, neither
you go into a complete collapse of super-ego.

00:16:38.100 --> 00:16:44.663
So much you know that any one of you can be
called as a scholar I can tell you.

00:16:44.663 --> 00:16:51.080
I mean so many times people have asked Me:
“Are they all scholars that You have – Your

00:16:51.080 --> 00:16:52.080
Disciples?”

00:16:52.080 --> 00:17:01.389
You know so much, much more than any Saint
ever knew I can assure you.

00:17:01.389 --> 00:17:03.440
But you know only in the brain, outside.

00:17:03.440 --> 00:17:06.010
It’s all bla bla bla.

00:17:06.010 --> 00:17:13.530
It comes to the brain, you use it to show
off to others, and finished.

00:17:13.530 --> 00:17:19.939
It doesn’t even settle down there, then
how will it go to the heart?

00:17:19.939 --> 00:17:26.209
So everybody is talking big, they can impress
people.

00:17:26.209 --> 00:17:32.860
I mean if some journalists come here they’ll
be so impressed by the Sahaja Yogis, so many

00:17:32.860 --> 00:17:39.620
wise men in England sitting down here.

00:17:39.620 --> 00:17:49.500
But you laugh at yourself; you have known
all this because I’ve been speaking too

00:17:49.500 --> 00:17:50.500
much.

00:17:50.500 --> 00:17:54.669
Also the Spirit is shining.

00:17:54.669 --> 00:18:06.240
Let your Spirit shine in such a way that people
know this is a man who is completely integrated:

00:18:06.240 --> 00:18:15.980
the Spirit, the talk, the behavior, the life
itself is completely integrated and this is

00:18:15.980 --> 00:18:16.980
what is Sahastrara.

00:18:16.980 --> 00:18:25.400
So if there is no integration you have not
achieved your Sahastrara.

00:18:25.400 --> 00:18:32.860
There will be no need to pull your ears.

00:18:32.860 --> 00:18:44.140
A day should come when you all will raise
your heads with great pride and glory because

00:18:44.140 --> 00:18:49.980
your ideals will shine like ornaments.

00:18:49.980 --> 00:18:56.480
I want to see those days when all those who
claim to be Sahaja Yogis become that.

00:18:56.480 --> 00:19:00.640
That’s the most important thing, all other
things are useless.

00:19:00.640 --> 00:19:07.500
Getting an ashram, getting this, doing this,
doing that – forget it.

00:19:07.500 --> 00:19:19.650
What you have to manage is this child which
has to grow, who is still naughty sometimes,

00:19:19.650 --> 00:19:20.650
tries to misbehave.

00:19:20.650 --> 00:19:21.880
Now put it right.

00:19:21.880 --> 00:19:24.090
You give it a name.

00:19:24.090 --> 00:19:29.960
You call yourself a Sahaja Yogi and that child
as Mr.

00:19:29.960 --> 00:19:30.960
X, Mr.

00:19:30.960 --> 00:19:36.660
Y whatever your name has been and always try
to tell: “Now will you behave yourself.

00:19:36.660 --> 00:19:42.060
” Get up in the morning, have your bath,
sit down for meditation.

00:19:42.060 --> 00:19:46.390
“I feel lazy,” the child says, “I can’t.

00:19:46.390 --> 00:19:51.590
” Then you accept the child, then the child
will become the mother and you will be losing

00:19:51.590 --> 00:19:53.010
your powers – excuses.

00:19:53.010 --> 00:20:03.330
The child knows, very intelligent, it’s
a very clever child, extremely intelligent,

00:20:03.330 --> 00:20:05.640
knows how to deceive you.

00:20:05.640 --> 00:20:13.169
But the child also knows innately what it
needs.

00:20:13.169 --> 00:20:19.870
If it comes to know that the mother in you
has developed that personality, then it accepts

00:20:19.870 --> 00:20:20.870
mother’s personality.

00:20:20.870 --> 00:20:27.320
But if the child knows the mother herself
is weak then he starts taking advantage of

00:20:27.320 --> 00:20:29.190
the mother.

00:20:29.190 --> 00:20:41.820
So you have to not fight yourself but to tame
and this is very easy.

00:20:41.820 --> 00:20:46.200
You’ll start enjoying it, looking at yourself:
“Oh Mr.

00:20:46.200 --> 00:20:47.669
so and so.

00:20:47.669 --> 00:20:49.240
” Then you won’t be angry.

00:20:49.240 --> 00:20:55.950
“I know how to handle you, you’re hiding
behind there, all right, giving excuses.

00:20:55.950 --> 00:21:09.860
” And the child grows big, so big that mother
sees that and is amazed.

00:21:09.860 --> 00:21:18.890
Like in Shri Krishna’s childhood, the Mother
was Yeshoda and the child was Shri Krishna.

00:21:18.890 --> 00:21:20.510
It’s very symbolic.

00:21:20.510 --> 00:21:30.200
And He used to play very naughty tricks and
She said: “You went and ate that mud from

00:21:30.200 --> 00:21:31.200
there.

00:21:31.200 --> 00:21:32.200
I know you have eaten.

00:21:32.200 --> 00:21:37.150
” He said: “How can I eat, how can I,
I can’t even go out of the house.

00:21:37.150 --> 00:21:38.820
I’m sitting down here.

00:21:38.820 --> 00:21:40.130
Where is the mud?

00:21:40.130 --> 00:21:42.090
How can I eat?”

00:21:42.090 --> 00:21:50.170
“You did eat, I know you have eaten, so
better show me your mouth.

00:21:50.170 --> 00:21:58.790
” He says: “Really?” and then the mouth
opens and the complete Vishwa Swarup, complete

00:21:58.790 --> 00:22:06.610
vision of the whole Vishwa She sees and the
Mother falls at His Feet.

00:22:06.610 --> 00:22:10.330
That’s what it should be.

00:22:10.330 --> 00:22:18.890
This mother has to fall at the feet of the
child that has grown.

00:22:18.890 --> 00:22:24.380
Very symbolic.

00:22:24.380 --> 00:22:31.419
That is how you have to grow, into that Vishwa
Swarup.

00:22:31.419 --> 00:22:39.179
Into that Collective Being, into that Virata.

00:22:39.179 --> 00:22:45.860
Arjuna and Shri Krishna is another very good
symbolic thing.

00:22:45.860 --> 00:22:52.690
Arjuna was a friend who used to take liberties
with Shri Krishna.

00:22:52.690 --> 00:23:02.570
Shri Krishna tried to tell him about Gita,
all these things.

00:23:02.570 --> 00:23:08.160
But still Shri Krishna could not convince
him of that.

00:23:08.160 --> 00:23:12.890
All these were just outside “bla bla bla’s”;
as Mother’s talks are.

00:23:12.890 --> 00:23:18.549
Mother’s talks are very entertaining you
know very humorous, nice to hear them, instead

00:23:18.549 --> 00:23:23.150
of listening to any music better to hear Mother’s
talks.

00:23:23.150 --> 00:23:27.360
And then the people think if they are listening
to Mother they have become Mother already.

00:23:27.360 --> 00:23:38.630
That’s it happened to Arjuna also but still
he found out that there’s something lacking

00:23:38.630 --> 00:23:41.710
in him, that he has not become the ideal.

00:23:41.710 --> 00:23:47.790
Still his attention is not there as it should
have been.

00:23:47.790 --> 00:23:54.619
